snippet.title: (Outdated Trailer) Whispering Hills - A Silenthill Overhaul for Fallout 4
snippet.description:
This is a small preview of Whispering hills. It starts with a fade into the otherworld, surviving it and shows the nighttime at the end too. 
You can find this mod inside of Fallout 4 modding directory on Bethesda.net
https://bethesda.net/de/mods/fallout4/mod-detail/4084253
